title: The Adjuster (1991, Atom Egoyan)
description:
Tagline: In search of relative comfort . . . . 

Plot summary (IMDb): A reflection about what makes everyone&#039;s life unique, through the story of Noah&#039;s family. Noah is an adjuster, having sex with his customers. His wife Hera watches pornographic movies for the Board of Censors. They live with their son Simon and Hera&#039;s sister in a show-flat. One day, they meet Bubba, who wants to make a movie in their house.
